originalText.text: I have been seeing Teddy for years for my chronic low back pain. I have seen dozens of doctors and tried everything from PT, to injections and yoga. Since my pain is mostly caused by muscle tightness, he does trigger point therapy on me where he sticks the needles into the tight muscles until they spasm. It hurts in the moment but feels amazing after, and it's the most relief I get for my back out of any of the other therapies I've tried. I highly recommend Teddy to anyone who has chronic muscular pain - he's significantly improved by quality of life.

originalText.text: I’ve been suffering from post-Covid symptoms for the last months (excessive fatigue, mental fogginess, short term memory issues), and Teddy is the reason I’ve been feeling so much better. Within one session I was already able to regain mental clarity. With two more following sessions, he’s also helped me with some stubborn neck, shoulder and lower back pain. He’s a magician. He’s incredibly gentle, calming and on point. I highly recommend him and can’t thank him enough for what he’s done for me!!

originalText.text: I have had excellent experiences working with Teddy. He is compassionate, smart and well versed in many different types of acupuncture . He has been helping me to rebalance my system and see me through post Covid symptoms. He has taken time to research my situation and has been an invaluable resource.

originalText.text: These days, it can be a real challenge to escape the stresses & anxiety of COVID which seem to land & live in the body. My experience with Teddy was a great shift from a gripping tension to a relaxed equanimity and sense of peace. What a wonderful relief.
